Pending that formalization, LLP and the LLP team are granted full
permission to use, deploy, modify, and operate the Platform for the
LLP business — including hosting, internal modifications, integration
with LLP's own services and accounts, and operational maintenance.

Redistribution outside the LLP business — including public release,
sublicensing, forking for unrelated projects, or use by third parties
not engaged with LLP — is reserved and requires the prior written
consent of Abs Rasel.

This notice is intended in the spirit of partnership and ongoing
collaboration rather than restriction. Questions, broader-use
